        "height": 672,
        "content": "### üì• Email Trigger (IMAP)\n\nThis node listens for new emails in your inbox and fetches PDF attachments.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n- Go to **Credentials** and create new IMAP credentials  \n- Fill in: IMAP host, port, email address, and password  \n- Optionally filter emails (e.g. only those with PDF attachments)\n"
