      "parameters": {
        "color": 6,
        "width": 816,
        "height": 800,
        "content": "### ü§ñ AI Data Extraction (Basic LLM Chain)\n\nThis node sends the text from the PDF to an AI model (e.g. GPT-4o) to extract structured invoice data.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n- Provide a clear prompt describing which data to extract  \n- Example: invoice number, dates, seller, buyer, tax number, total, currency  \n- Use JSON as the expected response format\n\n**Note:** \nIf the model fails to read some invoices (e.g. unusual layout, languages, or formats), try improving or customizing the prompt.\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
