        "color": 3,
        "width": 432,
        "height": 304,
        "content": "### üîë OpenAI API (LLM Provider)\n\nThis node connects to OpenAI (or another AI provider) and sends the invoice content for analysis.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n- Log in to [OpenAI](https://platform.openai.com) or your provider  \n- Generate an API key  \n- In **n8n**, create new credentials for the OpenAI node  \n- Select the correct model (`gpt-4o`, `gpt-3.5-turbo`, etc.)\n\n**Tip:** You can replace OpenAI with Anthropic, Mistral, or any compatible LLM node.\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
