        "content": "### üì§ Chat Notification (Discord Webhook)\n\nThis node sends a summary of the extracted invoice to your Discord channel.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n- In Discord:  \n  Go to Server Settings ‚Üí Integrations ‚Üí Webhooks ‚Üí Create Webhook  \n- Choose the target channel and copy the webhook URL  \n- Paste the URL into this node in n8n\n\n**Alternative:** \nSwap with Slack, Telegram, MS Teams, or another notification service.\n"
