        "height": 304,
        "content": "### ‚ùó Don't forget to set your PostgreSQL credentials\n\nIn every PostgreSQL-related node, you must manually select your own credentials from the dropdown.\n\n**Instructions:**\n- Click on the node  \n- Go to the **\"Credentials\"** section  \n- Select your custom PostgreSQL connection (e.g. `My Production DB`)  \n- Make sure the credentials have access to the correct database and tables\n\n‚ö†Ô∏è The workflow will fail if no credentials are selected or if the connection is invalid.\n"
