        "content": "### üîÄ Merge Node\n\nThis node merges metadata from the email (e.g., subject, sender) with the AI-extracted invoice content.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n- Input 1 ‚Üí AI output  \n- Input 2 ‚Üí Email data  \n- Set **Merge Strategy** to ‚ÄúMerge By Index‚Äù (if both inputs are aligned)\n\n**Use case:** \nAttach additional metadata (e.g., sender email) to your final record or notification.\n"
